author: Jamiee
text:
"Nightmares. Everyone is leaving me."
having to dream about ur fears is so tiring-

author: Jamiee
text:
"I smiled in my weakness."
and nobody noticed, nobody cared. it felt good that nobody noticed, while feeling like falling apart from the inside.

author: Jamiee
text: "As long as I can make them laugh, it doesn’t matter how, I’ll be alright. If I succeed in that, the human beings probably won’t mind it too much if I remain outside their lives."

author: Jamiee
text: "I'm so unwhole. I don't know where all the pieces of me are, how to fit them together, how to make them stick. Or if I even can."
